{"tid":1308701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【真唔真啊】Weconnect 侯強都去遊行聽日仲set水站","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T03:25:25.000Z","uid":254435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"50de6f92c0e31352a15105714c59f95baf90fbca","tid":1308701,"uid":254435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"侯稱，不論建制或泛民，日日都和不同人見面，不明白為什麼有人對於他與誰會面那麼執著。他說自己「樂見其成」，「能夠有更多人（示威者）來上水行行，表達意見，商戶及購物人士就會檢點，不要妨礙街坊，這是好事啊！」他強調歡迎任何人表達意見，從無叫人不要去遊行，「我支持合法、理性、守法遊行，但我不支持違法，包括互相指罵&hellip;&hellip;不理性的，自然有法律制裁，不關我事，我不是執法的」。他又稱自己曾參與6月9日、12日及16日的遊行示威，21日包圍警總也在外圍「湊熱鬧」 ，明日會在上水設站免費供應水。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190712/s00001/1562867615323/%e5%91%a8%e5%85%ad%e3%80%8c%e5%85%89%e5%be%a9%e4%b8%8a%e6%b0%b4%e3%80%8d%e7%94%b3%e8%ab%8b%e4%ba%ba-%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%ad%e9%96%93%e4%ba%ba%e3%80%8d%e6%b8%b8%e8%aa%aa%e5%8f%96%e6%b6%88-%e4%be%af%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%b7-%e5%92%8c%e5%b9%b3%e9%81%8a%e8%a1%8c%e6%a8%82%e8%a6%8b%e5%85%b6%e6%88%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190712%2Fs00001%2F1562867615323%2F%25e5%2591%25a8%25e5%2585%25ad%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2585%2589%25e5%25be%25a9%25e4%25b8%258a%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e3%2580%258d%25e7%2594%25b3%25e8%25ab%258b%25e4%25ba%25ba-%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e9%2596%2593%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%25b8%25b8%25e8%25aa%25aa%25e5%258f%2596%25e6%25b6%2588-%25e4%25be%25af%25e5%25bf%2597%25e5%25bc%25b7-%25e5%2592%258c%25e5%25b9%25b3%25e9%2581%258a%25e8%25a1%258c%25e6%25a8%2582%25e8%25a6%258b%25e5%2585%25b6%25e6%2588%2590&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0FGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=0357dbac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190712%2Fs00001%2F1562867615323%2F%25e5%2591%25a8%25e5%2585%25ad%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2585%2589%25e5%25be%25a9%25e4%25b8%258a%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e3%25